5 paragraph.
6 2. If:
7 a. The balance in the BRTF at the end of a fiscal year is equal to or
8 greater than ten percent (10%) of the GF moneys for that fiscal
9 year; and
10 b. GF moneys at the end of a fiscal year are equal to or greater than
11 GF appropriations for that fiscal year plus an amount that falls
12 within a range of greater than fifty percent (50%) but less than one
13 hundred percent (100%) of the IIT equivalent for that fiscal year;
14 then the tax rate reduction may be the current tax rate minus
15 twenty-five one-hundredths of one percent (0.25%).
16 3. If:
17 a. The balance in the BRTF at the end of a fiscal year is equal to or
18 greater than ten percent (10%) of the GF moneys for that fiscal
