20 b. GF moneys at the end of a fiscal year are equal to or greater than
21 GF appropriations for that fiscal year plus the IIT equivalent for
22 that fiscal year;
23 then the tax rate reduction may be the current tax rate minus five-
24 tenths of one percent (0.5%).
